<wi type="G" value="235,15,">sino</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2532,16,">que también</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4052,17,">abunda</wi>
<wi type="G" value="1223,18,">en</wi>
<wi type="G" value="4183,19,">muchos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="2169,20,">agradecimientos</wi>
<wi type="G" value="3588,21,"><wi type="G" value="2316,22,">a Dios</wi></wi>;</t>
</sv>
<sv id="2_Corintios-9-13">
seeing that through the
proof given by this service, they glorify God for the obedience of your
confession to the Good News of Christ, and for the liberality of your
contribution to them and to all;
